ning</strong> - Allocate resources to provide regular training and refresher courses for employees involved in manual handling tasks.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-2023_ pf-text-1"><strong>Review policies</strong> - Regularly review and update moving and handling policies to ensure compliance with legislation and best practice guidance.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-2025_ pf-text-1"><strong>Promote awareness</strong> - Raise awareness among employees about the importance of safe moving and handling practices through workshops, posters, and safety briefings.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-2027_ pf-text-1"><strong>Lead by example</strong> - Managers and supervisors should demonstrate and promote safe handling practices to their teams.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-2029_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2030_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-2031_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conclusion</h3><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-2033_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Effective moving and handling practices are essential for safeguarding the health and well-being of employees and maintaining a productive work environment. By prioritising training, implementing robust policies, and promoting a safety culture, businesses can reduce the risk of injuries, improve productivity, and ensure compliance with legislation. It's time to recognise the critical importance of effective moving and handling in UK settings and take proactive steps to protect workers' safety.<br><br>Are you looking to enhance your team's moving and handling skills? Explore our <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/moving-and-handling-courses-training" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">accredited training courses</span></em></a> today and ensure your workplace has the knowledge and expertise to promote safety and compliance.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2035_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Enhance_Workplace_Ergonomics_Professional_Moving_and_Handling_Training_Solutions_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1713349570" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Enhance_Workplace_Ergonomics_Professional_Moving_and_Handling_Training_Solutions_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1713349570 1536w" width="1000" height="645" alt="Enhance Workplace Ergonomics: Professional Moving and Handling Training Solutions - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Enhance Workplace Ergonomics: Professional Moving and Handling Training Solutions - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-2036_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-2037_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by nuttapong_mohock via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-193f" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-XxNYO gsQFwr pf-2039_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-dkYRCH hYpqjU"><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-2040_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2041_"><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-2042_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Moving and handling objects in workplaces across the UK is an everyday occurrence. From healthcare facilities to warehouses and construction sites, employees are regularly tasked with lifting, carrying, and moving objects of varying sizes and weights. However, many may need to realise the critical importance of compelling moving and handling practices in ensuring both workers' safety and businesses' smooth operation. In this blog, Rose Mabiza will explore why effective moving and handling is vital in UK settings, examining key facts, legislation, and best practices and offering recommendations for improvement.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-2044_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2045_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-2046_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-2048_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2049_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710431109" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710431109 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1710431109 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1710431109 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1710431109 320w" width="1612" height="1228" alt="Unlock Workplace Safety with Effective Handling Techniques and Risk Assessment - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Unlock Workplace Safety with Effective Handling Techniques and Risk Assessment - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-2050_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-2051_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by  Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-2053_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-2054_ pf-text-1">According to the Health and Safety Executive (HSE), manual handling injuries account for approximately 21% of all workplace injuries in the UK.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-2056_ pf-text-1">The HSE also reports that an estimated 6.9 million working days were lost due to work-related musculoskeletal disorders (MSDs) in 2020/21, with manual handling significantly contributing.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-2058_ pf-text-1">Manual handling practices result in physical injuries and increase absenteeism, decreased productivity, and financial losses for businesses.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-2060_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2061_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-2062_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key definitions</h3><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-2064_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-2065_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Health_and_Safety_Regulations_Manual_Handling_Operations_Regulations_Explained_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1094